tanding of wisdom and the ways to develop it.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aConduct of life. 0aPhilosophy. 0aReligions. 0aWisdom. 4aAnthropology and Archaeology : Anthropology. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy of Religion. 4aPsychology : Integral Theory. 4aPsychology : Psychology of Religion. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Religion. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh1 aWalsh, Roger, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143844959340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438449593423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438449593/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles